shults-directs-1236166595/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>截止日期</em></a>报道透露，这是他<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-reveals-artwork-for-new-album-hurry-up-tomorrow-3791679">即将发行的专辑的“延伸”，同样标题为“明天快点”</a> 。</p><p>据<em>Deadline</em>报道，这部电影已经拍摄完成，并由 The Weeknd（真名 Abel Tesfaye）主演。据报道，这部电影将是一部心理惊悚片，由<em>《夜来》</em>电影制片人特雷·爱德华·舒尔茨执导。 </p><figure id="attachment_3793331" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3793331" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3793331" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd@2000x1270.jpg" alt="The Weeknd 在巴西圣保罗演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/the-weeknd@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3793331" class="wp-caption-text">周末。图片来源：Pedro Vilela/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <em>Deadline</em>还报道称，The Weeknd 与 Daniel Lopatin（又名<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oneohtrix-point-never">Oneohtrix Point Never）</a>一起为电影配乐，后者此前曾与 Tesfaye 合作制作了他的 2022 年专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">Dawn FM</a> 》，并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-oneohtrix-point-nevers-remix-of-the-weeknds-song-dawn-fm-3265268">重新混音了主打歌</a>。</p><p> 《<em>快点明天》</em>电影尚未确定上映日期，但将通过狮门影业在全球发行。</p><p>狮门影业集团董事长亚当·福格尔森在给<em>Deadline</em>的一份声明中表示：“阿贝尔是一位有远见的人，他的艺术不能被任何单一媒介所限制。与 Trey 合作的<em>《快点明天》</em>将他的音乐宇宙扩展到大银幕，打造一部心理惊悚片，为影迷带来全新的电影体验。我们很高兴能够将其带给全世界的观众。”</p><p> Tesfaye 即将发行的专辑《Hurry Up Tomorrow》同样没有确定发行日期，但已经正式发行了三首单曲： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-weeknds-creepy-video-for-new-single-sao-paulo-featuring-anitta-3808247">《São Paulo》</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-weeknd-and-playboi-carti-team-up-on-new-single-timeless-3797591">《Timeless》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-walks-towards-the-light-in-new-dancing-in-the-flames-video-3793330">《Dancing In The Flames》</a> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3805356" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3805356" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3805356" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-weeknd@2000x1270.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-weeknd@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-weeknd@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-weeknd@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-weeknd@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-weeknd@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/the-weeknd@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3805356" class="wp-caption-text">周末。图片来源：Naomi Rahim/Getty Images for Live Nation</figcaption></figure><p>该唱片将成为以<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-after-hours-review-his-most-all-encompassing-record-to-date-is-also-an-existential-quandary-2632591">《After Hours》</a> （2020 年）和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-weeknd-dawn-fm-review-3132463">《Dawn FM》</a> （2022 年）开始的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-teases-return-with-after-hours-and-dawn-fm-sequel-3567220">三部曲的第三章，也是最后一章</a>。到目前为止，The Weeknd <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-shares-snippet-of-new-music-in-cinematic-teaser-3777326">最近已经预览了多首未发行的歌曲</a>，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-the-weeknd-played-at-his-special-sao-paulo-concert-3791657">《Wake Me Up》、《Take Me Back To LA》</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknd-previews-dancey-new-song-open-hearts-at-sydney-concert-3805355">《Open Hearts》</a> 。</p><p>在珍娜·奥尔特加 (Jenna Ortega) 方面，这位女演员目前正在拍摄 Netflix 热门剧集<a href="https://www.nme.com/series/wednesday"><em>周三</em></a>的第二季，最近主演了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/beetlejuice-beetlejuice-review-jenna-ortega-tim-burton-3791317"><em>《甲壳虫汁》(Beetlejuice Beetlejuice</em></a> )。</p><p>至于巴里·基奥根 (Barry Keoghan)，这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/saltburn-review-party-with-the-poshos-in-the-naughty-noughties-3541554"><em>索尔特伯恩</em></a>演员将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/barry-keoghan-gets-a-peaky-blinders-makeover-in-first-look-from-new-netflix-film-3808733">出现在即将上映的<em>《浴血黑帮》</em>电影中</a>，并且最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/fontaines-d-c-share-andrea-arnold-directed-video-for-bug-starring-barry-keoghan-franz-rogowski-nykiya-adams-and-more-3809351">主演了 Fontaines DC 的《Bug》音乐录影带</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-weeknds-upcoming-film-with-jenna-ortega-and-barry-keoghan-to-tie-into-hurry-up-tomorrow-album-3809535">The Weeknd 即将与珍娜·奥尔特加 (Jenna Ortega) 和巴里·基奥根 (Barry Keoghan) 合作的电影将与《Hurry Up Tomorrow》专辑搭配，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
